summary: Derrick Stewart, known as Fatman Scoop, a renowned rapper and DJ, has passed away at the age of 56. Onstage at a concert in Connecticut, Scoop collapsed, resulting in a medical emergency and subsequent hospitalization. His tragic death has sent shockwaves through the music industry, with Missy Elliott, Questlove, Ludacris, and other notable figures expressing their grief and condolences. Fatman Scoop, recognized for his Grammy-winning collaborations and energetic performances, will be remembered as an influential figure in hip-hop and dance music.
